&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-5669&quot; title=&quot;flink-streaming-contrib DataStreamUtils.collect in local environment mode fails when offline&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-5669&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-5669&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; Change DataStreamUtils to use the loopback address (127.0.0.1)&lt;/p&gt;

